@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Favorites";
}
<style>
    h1, h2, p
    {
        color:white;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .FavP
    {
        text-align:justify;
    }

    .FavImg 
    {
        width: 15vw;
        height: 40vh;
    }

    .column 
    {
        float: left;
        width: 25%;
    }

    /* Clear floats after the columns */
    .row:after 
    {
        content: "";
        display: table;
        clear: both;
    }

</style>

<h1 class ="display-5">Discover and geek out over the all-time favorite comics right here:"</h1>

<div class="row">
    <div class="column">
        <img class="FavImg" src="~/Images/Story1_Top.jpg" alt="Wizard"/>
        <h2>Chaos Reborn: The Pink Sorceress Chronicles</h2>
        <p class="FavP">
            In a world overrun by nightmarish creatures, a formidable female warrior with striking pink hair possesses a power unlike any other—green magic, a force that both sustains and destroys. She's not alone in her quest to save humanity from the encroaching darkness. At her side, a brilliant wizard, her loving husband, wields the arcane arts to combat the malevolent forces threatening their world.

            Together, they embark on a perilous journey, battling hordes of zombies and demons that plague their once-vibrant world. With every fight, they inch closer to unraveling the mystery of the insidious beast that threatens to consume everything in its path.

            As their powers grow, so do the stakes. The fate of their world hangs in the balance, and their determination to protect it fuels their unwavering resolve. But what is the true origin of the beast? And can they vanquish it before it engulfs their world in eternal darkness?
            "Chaos Reborn: The Pink Sorceress Chronicles" is a thrilling comic series that will leave readers on the edge of their seats, eager to uncover the secrets of the pink-haired sorceress and her wizard husband as they battle the forces of evil to save their world.
        </p>
        <img class="FavImg" src="~/Images/Story1_Bottom.jpg" alt="Pink Sorceress">
    </div>

    <div class="column">
        <img class="FavImg" src="~/Images/Story2_Top.jpg" alt="Poisonous Ivy 1">
        <h2>Ensnared by Nature's Embrace: The Poisonous Tale of Ivy</h2>
        <p class="FavP">
            In the heart of Gotham City, hidden away from the bustling streets and towering skyscrapers, lies a woman with fiery auburn hair and an aura of irresistible allure tends to her botanical wonders, each one more exotic and deadly than the last. She is Pamela Isley, but the world knows her as Poison Ivy.
            
            Pamela possesses the extraordinary ability to manipulate and control all things green. Her touch can be a soothing caress or a deadly kiss of venom. With the power of nature coursing through her veins, she has become both its guardian and its avenger. Beneath her emerald exterior lies a complex character, driven by a deep-seated love for the environment. 
            She views herself as Mother Nature's champion, determined to protect the earth from the destructive forces of humanity. Her crimes are often motivated by a twisted sense of ecological justice, where the line between hero and villain blurs.
            "Ensnared by Nature's Embrace: The Poisonous Tale of Ivy" is a captivating story that delves into the complexities of Pamela Isley's character and her extraordinary powers over plant life. As readers are drawn into her world, they will question whether she is a villain or a misunderstood eco-warrior, making it a compelling narrative that explores the blurred boundaries between good and evil.
        </p>
        <img class="FavImg" src="~/Images/Story2_Bottom.jpg" alt="Poisonous Ivy 2">
    </div>

    <div class="column">
        <img class="FavImg" src="~/Images/Story3_Top.new.jpg" alt="the Vox">
        <h2>The Secret Identities: Vox vs. The Skeleton King</h2>
        <p class="FavP">
            In the bustling metropolis of Nunez, a city plagued by both crime and superheroes, a unique secret kept the citizens on edge. In this world of caped crusaders and cunning villains, everyone wore a mask, and not just the ones made of cloth.
            The Skeleton King, a ruthless and enigmatic villain with an army of malevolent henchmen, posed a grave threat to the peace-loving inhabitants of Nunez. His aim was nothing short of domination, and he intended to conquer the land of mortals. 
            
            The city's only hope rested with a clandestine group known as the Vox, led by their fearless Lieutenant.
            What made the Vox special was their ability to transform. By day, they were ordinary citizens, leading ordinary lives. But by night, they became the city's protectors, using their unique powers and secret identities to thwart the Skeleton King's sinister plans.
            In a high-stakes mission filled with danger and intrigue, the Vox faced off against the Skeleton King and his formidable army of villains. With each confrontation, the lines between friend and foe blurred, and the true identities of those involved remained a closely guarded secret. 
            The fate of Nunez hung in the balance as the Lieutenant and the Vox group navigated this treacherous world of deception and heroism, determined to save their beloved city.
        </p>
        <img class="FavImg" src="~/Images/Story3_Bottom.jpg" alt="Skeleton King's army'">
    </div>

    <div class="column">
        <img class="FavImg" src="~/Images/Story4_Top.jpg" alt="The Warrior">
        <h2>The Warrior of Tsar Vaslav and the Green Apple Witch</h2>
        <p class="FavP">
            In the realm of Tsar Vaslav, a courageous warrior found himself transported to a world filled with wonder and danger. As he ventured through this mystical land, he encountered creatures straight out of legends – majestic unicorns, mischievous forest spirits, and wise old dragons. Each encounter brought new challenges and lessons, forging him into a formidable hero.
            But amidst the enchanting beauty, a shadow loomed. The evil Witch named Green Apple, feared by all, was rumored to be plotting something dark. Her sinister reputation sent shivers down the warrior's spine, and he knew that one day, their paths would inevitably cross.
            As he continued his journey, the warrior honed his skills, gathered allies from the magical creatures he met, and uncovered the hidden history of Tsar Vaslav. The clock was ticking, and he could feel the ominous presence of the Green Apple Witch drawing nearer. The fate of this fantastical world rested on his shoulders, and the warrior was determined to confront the witch and unveil the truth behind her wicked schemes.
        </p>
        <img class="FavImg" src="~/Images/Story4_Bottom.jpg" alt="Witch Green Apple">
    </div>
</div>